Introduction

My intention throughout the data collection process was to draw insights into peoples preferences regarding online streaming services and how those services shape their listening preferences/habits. As well as collecting information about their online music streaming habits, I have tried to deal with how long they stream music for and the reasons behind why.

Not only that, but being able to do this while adding new data is incredibly useful. I finally felt I was actually doing something related to Data Science, away from all the theory.

Though very simple, I tried to make use of indenting and assigning variables to make the code much clearer and more readable, both of which I also used in Assignment 1.
